{"tid":1748030,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］鉛水事件，民建聯成功爭取包庇中國建築公司","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:29:00.000Z","uid":217418,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31e63f43cc278c8ca63d4570f5f5c604bf6c296a","tid":1748030,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pentoy.hk/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E9%89%9B%E7%BD%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pentoy.hk%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2589%259B%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Ft5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=7ec54854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pentoy.hk/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E9%89%9B%E7%BD%AA/</a><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;第四宗罪：利益衝突，涉嫌包庇。蔣麗芸其丈夫梁海明，擔任啟晴總承建商中國建築的獨立非執行董事，並手持市值逾千萬的公司股票。但蔣氏在鉛水案之始不開誠佈公，甚至被傳媒揭發前，處處維護中國建築，抹黑踢爆真相的黃碧雲&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%89%9B%E6%B0%B4%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%89%AE-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91-%E6%94%94%E5%AE%98%E8%BB%8A%E6%B1%82%E9%A9%97%E6%B0%B4-%E9%99%B3%E6%81%92%E9%91%8C%E7%96%91-%E6%89%AF%E8%B2%93%E5%B0%BE-%E5%88%B6%E6%AD%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2589%259B%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2589%25AE-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E6%2594%2594%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%25A9%2597%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2581%2592%25E9%2591%258C%25E7%2596%2591-%25E6%2589%25AF%25E8%25B2%2593%25E5%25B0%25BE-%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25AD%25A2%2F&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Ft5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=ef6c591c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2589%259B%2